data.description: True 4 bedroom 3 bath home on corner lot. HUGE family room with wood burning frplc. Kitchen has lots of cabinet/counter space & all appliances stay (range/oven is gas & has a double oven). Previous owners had used the formal living room as the dining room making plenty of room for entertaining. Informal dining room was used as a coffee bar. Huge master bedroom with walk in closet & full bath with whirlpool tub, shower, double sinks.  Water softener & front load washer & dryer included. Some newer windows, new roof & gutters 2021. Water Heater 2017. Nice and quiet belt drive garage door opener. Whole house fan. Extra wide and long driveway. Don't miss checking out this great house! Fresh interior paint & some new carpet. Newer wood privacy fence, newer deck, nicely terraced back yard with great spot for an evening by the firepit. Check out the Open Houses this weekend! AMA.
